Alembic migrations for the EUDR platform.

The connection URL comes from the application settings (DATABASE_URL / .env),
not from alembic.ini; see env.py. Common commands, from the project root:

    ./venv/bin/alembic upgrade head
    ./venv/bin/alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe the change"
    ./venv/bin/alembic check          # fails if models and migrations diverge

Development still uses create_all on startup for convenience; production owns
its schema exclusively through these migrations.
